OL,3,C'He licked the knife': Man tries to
OL,4,Csmash glass door before being shot by
OL,5,Cpolice
OL,7,FBodycam footage of Marius Ciolac
OL,8,Fsmashing a window and attacking police
OL,9,Fcars at Ascot Drive police station in
OL,10,FDerby
OL,12,FA police officer has told an inquest
OL,13,Fjury how a man armed with a knife
OL,14,Fappeared to lick the blade minutes
OL,15,Fbefore a firearms officer shot him at
OL,16,Fa police station.
