OL,3,C'He licked the knife': Man tries to
OL,4,Csmash glass door before being shot by
OL,5,Cpolice
OL,7,FMarius Ciolac brandished a 20cm-long
OL,8,Fknife while "bizarrely" carrying a cat
OL,9,Fin a bag in the car park of Ascot
OL,10,FDrive police station n Derby on 7
OL,11,FOctober 2022, Derby Coroner's Court
OL,12,Fheard on Thursday.
OL,14,FThe jury heard the 35-year-old, who
OL,15,Fworked as a builder, entered the
OL,16,Fpolice station compound through a
OL,17,Fsliding metal gate at around 10 am
OL,18,Fbefore a Taser, a baton round and a
OL,19,Fstun grenade were used, and Mr Ciolac
OL,20,Fwas shot in the abdomen minutes later.
