OL,7,FMr Ciolac, originally from Romania,
OL,8,Fwas given medical aid by paramedics at
OL,9,Fthe scene but went into cardiac arrest
OL,10,Fand was taken to Queen's Medical
OL,11,FCentre in Nottingham, where he died at
OL,12,F11.25 am.
OL,14,F"There was no doubt if he got inside
OL,15,Fthe station he would have stabbed me."
