OL,7,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,8,FConduct (IOPC) previously said
OL,9,Fofficers had used a stun grenade,
OL,10,Fbaton round and Taser in an attempt to
OL,11,Fstop Mr Ciolac after reports windows
OL,12,Fhad been smashed and a man had been
OL,13,Fseen with a knife.
OL,15,FSergeant Anthony England was in the
OL,16,Fstation building with other officers
OL,17,Fwhen Mr Ciolac broke through the first
OL,18,Flayer of the double-glazed window.
