OL,7,FHe said: "He put his face against the
OL,8,Fglass and appeared to lick the knife.
OL,9,FIt was quite bizarre and horrible.
OL,11,F"He tried to stab the doors again to
OL,12,Fbreak the second layer. There was no
OL,13,Fdoubt if he got inside the station, he
OL,14,Fwould have stabbed me or one of the
OL,15,Fofficers with the knife he had.
OL,17,F"The concern was about my colleagues.
OL,18,FMy main concern was him getting out of
OL,19,Fthat compound... and members of the
OL,20,Fpublic he could easily get to.
