OL,7,F"I asked for his name and why he was
OL,8,Fdoing this but I could not hear him
OL,9,Fclearly. He appeared to have an
OL,10,Feastern European accent but I could
OL,11,Fnot understand him."
OL,13,FSgt England described to the jury the
OL,14,Fmoment he saw a pet carrier rucksack
OL,15,Fwith a clear front and a cat inside.
OL,17,FHe said: "There was a bag to the side
OL,18,Fwhich bizarrely had the cat inside.
OL,19,FAfter everything that just happened, I
OL,20,Fwas surprised to see the cat.
