OL,7,F"I believe the cat was ok, it was fine
OL,8,Fas far as I understand. It was just
OL,9,Fvery, very bizarre behaviour."
OL,11,FThe IOPC said in 2022 that three
OL,12,Fknives of various sizes were recovered
OL,13,Ffrom the scene, along with a cat in a
OL,14,Fbag.
OL,16,FDerbyshire Police said after the
OL,17,Fincident the cat was safe and was
OL,18,Ftaken into the care of a cat centre.
OL,20,FThe inquest continues, and is expected
OL,21,Fto run into February.
